@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_oobnvv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.65
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.sin((v0 + 0.43 - v2 + 0.30)))
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.abs(tmp + 0.74) * (tmp + 0.61 * v0 + 0.17)))
    v0 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.61 - v1 + 0.74)) + ((v2 + 0.30 + v1 + 0.18) - 0.18))
    data[tid] = v0
